Hangout.Server.WebServices.PayPalCallBackHandlerThis implements the callback method from PayPal to complete the purchase process. This functions expects the XML result from the callback page in the following form: There are 3 return types: PaypalReturn ==> succesfully charged the card. PaypalCancel ==> user canceled the transaction PaypalRecurring ==> a recurring transaction was succesfully initiated. In each case the twofish service needs to be called to comlete the transaction. The parameters used to call twofish are the return paramaters from the callback
